        "name": "Wall of Shrubs",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You call forth a line of bushes native to the region to spring from the ground. The wall of shrubs stands in a line 60 feet long, is less than 5 feet tall, and is a foot thick, providing lesser cover.",
